This is the Category The Great Outdoors of Ontario!

Questions:
What kind of tree is most common in Ontario's Wilderness?
Spruce
What is Ontario's provincial bird?
Loon
What antler-bearing animal is common in Ontario's Wilderness?
Deer
In Ontario, what direction must you travel to get to the Wilderness?
North
What Wilderness Biome is most of ontario?
Forest
What is the name of the massive body of water that is north of ontario?
James Bay
Ontario is the most populated province in canada (True/False).
True
Only a tiny fraction of ontario is populated (True/False).
True
What is the name of the organization that works within ontario to preserve wetlands?
Ducks Unlimited
What is the name of ontario's most famous provincial park?
Algonquin